    <text>
        <body>
            <div>
                <head type="title"><app>
                    <lem wit="#KK #M">Index XIII.</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#P">Index IIII.</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#B">Index XVIII.</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #R">Index XII.</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#L1 #L2">Index XIII., in quo regnum Colimani ostenditur</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#S1 #S2 #S3">Index XII. de Colimano rege eiusque crudelitate</rdg>
                    </app></head>
                <p>
                <s n="1">﻿Huic regi nulli 
                    <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #L1">(
                            <app>
                                <lem wit="#KK #P">cum</lem>
                                <rdg wit="#B"/>
                                <rdg wit="#L1">quod</rdg>
                            </app> vitam 
                            <app>
                                <lem wit="#KK #L1">egerit</lem>
                                <rdg wit="#P #B">aegerit</rdg>
                            </app> caelibem)
                        </lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">
                            <app>
                                <rdg wit="#Z">cum</rdg>
                                <rdg wit="#R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">quod</rdg>
                            </app> vitam egerit 
                        </rdg>
                    </app>  
                    <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #L1">caelibem)</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#L2">caelibem</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #R #S1 #S2 #S3">coelibem</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#M">celibem</rdg>
                    </app> liberi fuere, at 
                    <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #R #M">Geisa</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#L1">Geiissa</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#L2 #S1 #S2 #S3">Geysa</rdg>
                    </app> eius frater duos reliquerat filios, Colimanum et Almum, eos moriens <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B">(parvuli nanque tum erant)</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">parvuli namque <app>
                                <rdg wit="#Z #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">tum</rdg>
                                <rdg wit="#L1 #L2">tunc</rdg>
                            </app> erant</rdg>
                    </app> Ladislai commiserat fidei.<app>
                        <lem wit="#B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M"/>
                        <rdg wit="#P"><note type="marginalia">Colimanus rex .IX</note></rdg>
                    </app></s>
                <s n="2">Ladislaus autem, cum ei mors immineret, quia Colimanus ob nimiam corporis
                    deformitatem pravitatemque ingenii nequaquam fuerat ei visus ad regnum idoneus,
                    cohortatus est eos, quorum curae res incumbebat, ut se mortuo Almum quam
                    Colimanum mallent regno praeficere.</s>
                <s n="3">Secus si fecerint, hoc habeant futuras esse complurium innoxiorum hominum <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">caedes</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#P">cedes</rdg>
                    </app>, inter consanguineos magna dissidia capitaliaque odia, sacrilegia aliaque
                    permulta impietatis genera, divino se <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">afflatum</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#P">affatum</rdg>
                    </app> spiritu talia vaticinari.<note type="critic" corresp="RKK">1–3 = Th 2.59.
                        – Verba prima (<hi rend="italic">Huic... nulli... liberi fuere</hi> et de
                        caelibatu dicta) ostendunt Ransanum non recte intellexisse, quod Thuróczy de
                        vitae sanctitate Ladislai scripsisset, nam filiam nomine Pyrisk et Th 2.63
                        memorat.</note></s>
                <s n="4"><app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Ceterum</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#P #B #Z #L1 #R #L2">Caeterum</rdg>
                    </app> eo mortuo Hungari quisque sua secuti studia, quae vir sanctus
                    praemonuerat, prorsus neglexere.</s>
                <s n="5">Colimanus morte regis <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">accepta</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#P #B">accaepta</rdg>
                    </app> ex Polonia, ubi tunc agebat, illico venit in Hungariam.</s>
                <s n="6"><app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #L1 #L2">Coacto</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Coactoque</rdg>
                    </app> paulo post ipsius adventum totius regni senatu, ubi satis est agitatum,
                    uter fratrum esset regno <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">praeficiendus</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#P">preficiendus</rdg>
                    </app>, Almus <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B">(cum esset vir miti ingenio)</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">cum esset vir miti <app>
                                <rdg wit="#L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">ingenio</rdg>
                                <rdg wit="#Z">ingenuo</rdg>
                            </app></rdg>
                    </app>, quod erat natu minor, Colimano <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">cessit</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#P #B">caessit</rdg>
                    </app>, qui magna omnium <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">laetitia</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #L1">laeticia</rdg>
                    </app> rex appellatus <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">regium</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B"><del>regnum</del>regium</rdg>
                    </app> de more diadema <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">suscepit</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#P #B">suscaepit</rdg>
                    </app>.</s>
                <s n="7">Ante vero omnia Almum et nomine et dignitate ducis honoravit.</s>
                <s n="8">Fuit quidem primum inter ipsos summus rerum omnium consensus, deinde vero
                    assentatorum malignitate effectum est, ut dum vixerunt, odiis inter se <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">decertaverint</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B"><del>decaetaverunt</del>decaetaverint</rdg>
                    </app>
                    <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">implacabilibus</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B #Z #L1 #L2">inplacabilibus</rdg>
                    </app>.</s>
                <s n="9">Sub eo Hungari multa gravia deoque et mortalibus quam molestissima perpessi
                    sunt, multa enim inique <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3">atque</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#M">et</rdg>
                    </app> crudeliter gessit, nec evenit aliter, quam quod <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">beatus</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z">beatns</rdg>
                    </app> Ladislaus moriens deo <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #L1 #L2">(ut diximus)</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">ut diximus</rdg>
                    </app> inspirante <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #R #L2">praenunciaverat</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B #L1 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">praenuntiaverat</rdg>
                    </app>.<note type="critic" corresp="RKK">4–9 = Th 2.60. – 9 <hi rend="italic">ut
                            diximus</hi> cf. Index XIII.2–3.</note></s>
                <s n="10">Sed praetermissis <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #L2 #S3 #M">ceteris</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#P">coeteris</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#B #Z #L1 #R #S1 #S2">caeteris</rdg>
                    </app> ea solum perstringam scelera, <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">quae</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">que</rdg>
                    </app> in fratrem <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">nepotemque</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B #L1 #L2">nepotem</rdg>
                    </app> commisit.</s>
                <s n="11">Post longi temporis dissidia, <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P">quom</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">cum</rdg>
                    </app> ad pacem iam venissent, cuius componendae gratia Romanorum imperator e
                    Germania venerat in Hungariam, essetque ea pax iureiurando firmata, <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B">quom primum</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">cum primum</rdg>
                    </app> imperator domum regressus est, iussit rex <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #L1 #L2">effodi</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #R">capi</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#S1 #S2 #S3 #M">eos capi</rdg>
                    </app>
                    <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">effossosque</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z">effososque</rdg>
                    </app>
                    <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3">utriusque</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#M"/>
                    </app>
                    <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #L1 #L2">illorum oculos</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">oculos illorum</rdg>
                    </app> ad se deferri.</s>
                <s n="12">Huic crudelitati aliud adiecit scelus.</s>
                <s n="13">Nepotis <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B">nanque</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">namque</rdg>
                    </app>, hoc est filii Almi, qui <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">tum</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#L2">tunc</rdg>
                    </app> erat infantulus Bela nomine, iussit <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #L1 #L2">abscidi</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">abscindi</rdg>
                    </app>
                    <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">genitalia</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#P">genitaliã</rdg>
                    </app>, ne ei in regnum succederet ad gignendos <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">videlicet filios</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#L1 #L2">filios videlicet</rdg>
                    </app> factus inhabilis.<app>
                        <lem wit="#P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M"/>
                        <rdg wit="#B"><note type="marginalia"><gap unit="word"
                            extent="unknown"/> facinus</note>
                        </rdg>
                    </app></s>
                <s n="14"><app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Ceterum</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#P #B #Z #L1 #R #L2">Caeterum</rdg>
                    </app> ille, cuius curae demandata res est, sceleratae iussioni non paruit,
                    dixit nihilominus regi <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3">executum</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#M">exsecutum</rdg>
                    </app> se diligenter fuisse, quod iusserat, at vero ille abscidit testes catuli,
                    qui eum sequebatur, quos regi ostendens, En, inquit, <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P">Belae</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M"/>
                    </app> testes, quos <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #R #L2">abscidi</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#S1 #S2 #S3 #M">abscindi</rdg>
                    </app> tibi voluisti, cui <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #R #L2 #S1 #S3 #M">Colimanus</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#L1">Colmianus</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#S2">Colomanus</rdg>
                    </app> habuit fidem.</s>
                <s n="15">Eo enim ille regis noluit obtemperare imperio, quod veritus est, ne, si
                    obtemperasset, regium postea genus omnino <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3">extingueretur</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#M">exstingueretur</rdg>
                    </app>.</s>
                <s n="16"><app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Ceterum</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#P #B #Z #L1 #R #L2">Caeterum</rdg>
                    </app> Almi fratris nec etiam vitae Colimanus pepercit.</s>
                <s n="17"><app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #M">Struxerat is</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#S2">Struxeratis</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#S3">Struxerat</rdg>
                    </app> Demesiense monasterium, quo postea, quam <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #L2 #M">excaecatus</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #R #S1 #S2 #S3">excoecatus</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#L1">excecatus</rdg>
                    </app> ab illo fuit, se contulit, ut ibi vitam et ageret et decreto a deo
                    tempore finiret.</s>
                <s n="18">Inter haec rex incidit in mirum ac miserabile morbi genus, quo cerebrum <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #L1 #L2">eius paulatim</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">paulatim eius</rdg>
                    </app> fluebat ex auribus.</s>
                <s n="19">Itaque intelligens morti se esse propinquum accersito ad se filio, de quo
                    paulo post <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B">fiet mihi sua</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">fiet mihi</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#L1 #L2">mihi fiet</rdg>
                    </app> mentio, ac aliis multis, quibus <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">fidebat</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">fide-<note type="critic">B textus interrumpitur, foll. 6
                                sequentia deperdita sunt</note></rdg>
                    </app><app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">, iubet eis, ut dent operam,
                            qua Almus interficiatur.</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B"/>
                    </app></s>
                            <s n="20">Id imperium si <app>
                                    <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3">exequi</lem>
                                    <rdg wit="#M">exsequi</rdg>
                                </app> neglexerint, haudquaquam dubitandum, quin se mortuo ille sit
                                in regnum successurus.</s>
                            <s n="21">Nec mora continuo mittitur, qui illum in ecclesia monasterii,
                                cuius memini, ad sanctae <app>
                                    <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #M">Margaritae</lem>
                                    <rdg wit="#S3">Margarithae</rdg>
                                </app> altare, ad quod salutis causa confugerat <app>
                                    <lem wit="#KK #P #L1 #L2">(putaverat enim fore, ut ob sacri loci
                                        reverentiam ille <app>
                                            <lem wit="#KK #P">tanto</lem>
                                            <rdg wit="#L1 #L2"/>
                                        </app>
                                        <app>
                                            <lem wit="#KK #L1 #L2">abstineret</lem>
                                            <rdg wit="#P">abstineret<del><add type="insert">
                                                  imperio</add></del><note type="critic">P addit et
                                                  del.</note></rdg>
                                        </app> nefario)</lem>
                                    <rdg wit="#Z #R #S1 #S2 #S3">putaverat enim fore, ut ob sacri
                                        loci reverentiam ille <app>
                                            <rdg wit="#Z #R">tanto</rdg>
                                            <rdg wit="#S1 #S2 #S3">facto</rdg>
                                        </app> abstineret nefario</rdg>
                                    <rdg wit="#M">— putaverat enim fore, ut ob sacri loci
                                        reverentiam ille facto abstineret nefario —</rdg>
                                </app><!--ellenőrizendő  -->, <app>
                                    <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #R">interemit</lem>
                                    <rdg wit="#L1 #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">interimat</rdg>
                                </app>.</s>
                            <s n="22"><app>
                                    <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Benedicto</lem>
                                    <rdg wit="#L2">Benedictus</rdg>
                                </app> erat illi nomen, qui tam grande admisit scelus, at non impune
                                quidem, <app>
                                    <lem wit="#KK #P #Z">nanque</lem>
                                    <rdg wit="#L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">namque</rdg>
                                </app>, cum loci sacerdotes fugientem illum insequerentur, equo, quo
                                vehebatur, delapsus effracta cervice repente <app>
                                    <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3">extinctus</lem>
                                    <rdg wit="#M">exstinctus</rdg>
                                </app> est, eius autem corpus canes, quos secum ipse duxerat,
                                protinus dilacerarunt <app>
                                    <lem wit="#KK #P #L1 #L2">devoraruntque</lem>
                                    <rdg wit="#Z #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">devoraveruntque</rdg>
                                </app>.</s>
                            <s n="23">Rex quoque laborans ex morbo, quem dixi, diem impie <app>
                                    <lem wit="#KK #P #L1 #L2">(ut vixerat)</lem>
                                    <rdg wit="#Z #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">ut vixerat</rdg>
                                </app> obiit anno ab ortu Iesu Christi <app>
                                    <lem wit="#KK #P #L1 #L2">MCXIIII</lem>
                                    <rdg wit="#Z #M">M.C.XIII.</rdg>
                                    <rdg wit="#R #S1 #S2 #S3">millesimo centesimo decimo
                                        tertio</rdg>
                                </app> tertio Nonas <app>
                                    <lem wit="#KK #P">Februarias</lem>
                                    <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Februarii</rdg>
                                </app>.</s>
                            <s n="24">Regnavit annos quinque et <app>
                                    <lem wit="#KK #P">XX</lem>
                                    <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">viginti</rdg>
                                </app>, <app>
                                    <lem wit="#KK #P">menses</lem>
                                    <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">mensesque</rdg>
                                </app>
                                <app>
                                    <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3">sex</lem>
                                    <rdg wit="#M">rex</rdg>
                                </app>.<note type="critic" corresp="RKK">10–24 = Th 2.62. – 21 <hi
                                        rend="italic">cuius memini</hi> cf. Index XIII.17. – 23 <hi
                                        rend="italic">quem dixi</hi> cf. Index XIII.18.</note></s>
                            <s n="25">Duas duxit uxores, ex earum una duos <app>
                                    <lem wit="#KK #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">suscepit</lem>
                                    <rdg wit="#P">suscaepit</rdg>
                                </app> filios, Ladislaum et Stephanum, <app>
                                    <lem wit="#KK #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">quorum</lem>
                                    <rdg wit="#P">quarum</rdg>
                                </app> matre <app>
                                    <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">mortua</lem>
                                    <rdg wit="#L1">mortuo</rdg>
                                </app> duxit alteram natione <app>
                                    <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2">Rhutenam</lem>
                                    <rdg wit="#S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Ruthenam</rdg>
                                </app>, quam, cum <app>
                                    <lem wit="#KK #Z #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">deprehendisset</lem>
                                    <rdg wit="#P #L1">depraehendisset</rdg>
                                </app> in adulterio, remisit ad parentes.<note type="critic"
                                    corresp="RKK">25 = Th 2.60–61.</note></s>
                            <s n="26">Fuit in rebus <app>
                                    <lem wit="#KK #P #L1 #L2">gestis</lem>
                                    <rdg wit="#Z #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">gerendis</rdg>
                                </app> admodum prudens et fortunatus plurimum.</s>
                            <s n="27"><app>
                                    <lem wit="#KK #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Subegit</lem>
                                    <rdg wit="#P">Subaegit</rdg>
                                </app> Dalmatas Petro eorum rege <app>
                                    <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2">interempto</lem>
                                    <rdg wit="#S1 #S2 #S3 #M">interemto</rdg>
                                </app>, qui eam regionem mortuo beato Ladislao sibi occupaverat
                                ipsis Dalmatis non invitis.</s>
                            <s n="28">Mercede conduxit instructissimam a Venetis classem, quam misit
                                in Apuliam, per quam excurrentes Hungari magnam eius partem <app>
                                    <lem wit="#KK #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">caede</lem>
                                    <rdg wit="#P">cede</rdg>
                                </app> et incendiis multorumque generum <app>
                                    <lem wit="#KK #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">praeda</lem>
                                    <rdg wit="#P">preda</rdg>
                                </app> vastavere, expugnaverunt ac diripuerunt <app>
                                    <lem wit="#KK #P">Monopolim ac</lem>
                                    <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Monopolim et</rdg>
                                </app> Brundusium, quae <app>
                                    <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #M">clarae</lem>
                                    <rdg wit="#S2 #S3">clare</rdg>
                                </app> tum erant suntque hodie in ea regione urbes, tenebantur
                                ditione Roberti <app>
                                    <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Guiscardi</lem>
                                    <rdg wit="#L2">Giuscardi</rdg>
                                </app>, cuius viri fortia facta supra <app>
                                    <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #M">explicata</lem>
                                    <rdg wit="#S2 #S3">explicanda</rdg>
                                </app> sunt, ubi visus est <app>
                                    <lem wit="#KK #P #L1 #L2">suus</lem>
                                    <rdg wit="#Z #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">aptus</rdg>
                                </app> hortari locus.<note type="critic" corresp="RKK">26–28 <hi
                                        rend="italic">Brundusium</hi> = Th 2.62.</note></s>
                            <s n="29">Ad ipsum ut primum rei perlata est fama, missis terra marique
                                copiis, quas amiserat, urbes recuperavit, classem praeterea iussit
                                proficisci ad oras Dalmaticas, quae facta per multa loca excursione
                                non minora Robertus intulit hosti quam illa, quae <app>
                                    <lem wit="#KK #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">acceperat</lem>
                                    <rdg wit="#P">accaeperat</rdg>
                                </app>, detrimenta.<note type="critic" corresp="RKK">28 quae clarae... 29<hi rend="italic">
                                        <note type="editorial">...</note>detrimenta</hi>
                                    <p>cf. Annales vol. III. fol. 317v: „A Capua distat urbs Adversa
                                            <hi rend="overline">VIII</hi> P., quae nova est, condita
                                        videlicet anno abhinc [<hi rend="italic">locus numeri
                                            vacat</hi>] a viro fortissimo Roberto Guiscardo, ut
                                        quidam tradunt, cuius habebo mentionem libro huius operis
                                            [<hi rend="italic">locus numeri vacat</hi>], quo sum
                                        scripturus seriem eorum, qui in Sicilia insula et in regno,
                                        quod dicitur Neapolitanum imperium, a priscis temporibus ad
                                        haec usque nostra tempora tenuerunt.“ In marg. manu Thomae
                                        Fazello: „quod non scripsit, utinam, autem
                                        scripsisset“.</p><p>Ibidem foll. 484v–485r: „Vitalis Falero
                                        doge classem potentissimam misit adversus Rogerium
                                        Guiscardum, qui litorales quasdam urbes ad oram Adriatici
                                        maris sitas Alexii Graecorum imperatoris imperio parentes
                                        invadebat atque vastabat. Quae classis cum navigiis aliquot
                                        Graecorum coniuncta, adorta Guiscardi classem post commissam
                                        atrocissimam pugnam victoriam adepta est [<hi rend="italic"
                                            >del.</hi> eo] fugato compulsoque hoste, ut eo, unde
                                        venerat, inglorius regrederetur.“</p></note></s>
                            <s n="30">Hactenus de Colimano, hinc, quisnam <app>
                                    <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3">illi</lem>
                                    <rdg wit="#M">ei</rdg>
                                </app> successerit, ostendamus.</s>
                        
            </p>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
